Ingredients are:
Glue

Borax (1tsp dissolved in 1cup hot water) or Tide or Sta Flo liquid starch
Stirring things:
Spatula
Food processor (if u r stoopid)
Bowl
1. Pour in glue in bowl
2. Add shaving cream, lotion and foam beads and stir
3. Add borax (not too much or slime turns out like slippy putty) until non-sticky.
You will need white Elmers glue for this fluffy foam (floam) slime recipe!
